---
// About.astro — Sobre mí section
---

<section class="section about" id="sobre-mi">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-label">01. sobre mí</span>
    </div>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <!-- Left: Timeline -->
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>

        <div class="timeline-item" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
          <div class="timeline-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <span class="timeline-year">2025 – Presente</span>
            <h3 class="timeline-role">Software Engineer Intern</h3>
            <div class="timeline-company">Notaria PAINO · Remoto</div>
            <ul class="timeline-details">
              <li class="timeline-desc">
                Desarrollo y mantenimiento continuo de sistemas internos enfocados en la automatización de flujos de trabajo y procesos notariales, utilizando tecnologías como Python, Node.js, Selenium y Playwright.
              </li>
              <li class="timeline-desc">
                Programé y mantuve APIs internas, integrando servicios de base de datos para la gestión eficiente de documentos.
              </li>
              <li class="timeline-desc">
                Reduje el ciclo de procesamiento de datos mediante scripts personalizados de scraping, mejorando la disponibilidad de información para el área legal.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Bio + principles -->
      <div class="about-right">
        <blockquote class="about-quote">
          <div class="quote-glyph" aria-hidden="true">//</div>
          <p class="quote-text">
            Me adapto rápido a cualquier entorno laboral, apoyándome en mi flexibilidad para 
            aprender una tecnología o las reglas de negocio de tu empresa.
          </p>
          <footer class="quote-footer">
            <span class="quote-author">Fernando Olivera</span>
            <span class="quote-role">Backend Developer</span>
          </footer>
        </blockquote>

        <div class="about-text">
          <p>
            Cuento con 1+ años de experiencia en Java y Node.js,
            especializado en sistemas distribuidos, APIs REST y automatización
            de procesos con IA.
          </p>
          <p>
            Estoy buscando incorporarme a un equipo donde pueda contribuir desde 
            el día uno, aprender de arquitecturas en producción
            a gran escala y crecer hacia roles de mayor responsabilidad técnica.
          </p>
          <!-- Cloud versatility chips -->
          <div class="cloud-chips">
            <span class="cloud-label">Cloud &amp; Infra</span>
            <div class="cloud-tags">
              <span class="cloud-tag">AWS EC2</span>
              <span class="cloud-tag">AWS SES</span>
              <span class="cloud-tag cloud-tag--dev">AWS S3</span>
              <!--<span class="cloud-tag">AWS Lambda</span>-->
              <span class="cloud-tag cloud-tag--dev">Kubernetes</span>
              <span class="cloud-tag cloud-tag--dev">Docker</span>
              <span class="cloud-tag cloud-tag--dev">RabbitMQ</span>
              <!--<span class="cloud-tag cloud-tag--dev">Terraform</span>-->
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Principles grid -->
        <div class="principles">
          
          <div class="principle-card">
            <div class="principle-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4>Performance First</h4>
            <p>La latencia no es un detalle — es un requisito de negocio.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="principle-card">
            <div class="principle-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle>
                <path d="M19.07 4.93a10 10 0 0 1 0 14.14M4.93 4.93a10 10 0 0 0 0 14.14"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4>Automatización</h4>
            <p>Si se repite más de dos veces, se automatiza.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="principle-card principle-card--cloud">
            <div class="principle-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M18 10h-1.26A8 8 0 1 0 9 20h9a5 5 0 0 0 0-10z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4>Cloud-Native</h4>
            <p>Despliegues en AWS con Docker, lambdas y colas de mensajes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Timeline */
  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 901px) {
    .timeline {
      position: sticky;
      top: calc(68px + var(--space-8));
      align-self: start;
    }
  }

  .timeline-line {
    position: absolute;
    left: 7px;
    top: 12px;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--cyan), transparent);
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-5);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-8);
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s var(--ease-out) both;
  }

  .timeline-dot {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 15px;
    height: 15px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--canvas);
    border: 2px solid var(--cyan);
    margin-top: 3px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    transition:
      background var(--t-fast),
      box-shadow var(--t-fast);
  }

  .timeline-item:hover .timeline-dot {
    background: var(--cyan);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--cyan-glow);
  }

  .timeline-content {
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .timeline-year {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    color: var(--cyan);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }

  .timeline-role {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .timeline-company {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .timeline-details {
    list-style-type: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2.5);
  }

  .timeline-desc {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--ink-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: var(--space-4);
  }

  .timeline-desc::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--cyan);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
  }

  /* Right side */
  .about-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-8);
    animation: fadeUp 0.7s var(--ease-out) 0.15s both;
  }

  .about-quote {
    position: relative;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.06) 0%, rgba(13, 32, 60, 0.8) 100%);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--r-xl);
    padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-6) var(--space-5);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 0 32px rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.04);
  }

  .about-quote::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: var(--r-xl);
    padding: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), transparent 60%);
    -webkit-mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
    -webkit-mask-composite: xor;
    mask-composite: exclude;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .quote-glyph {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    color: var(--cyan);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .quote-text {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .quote-footer {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    padding-top: var(--space-3);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-ghost);
  }

  .quote-author {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    color: var(--cyan);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .quote-role {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .quote-role::before {
    content: '·';
    margin-right: var(--space-3);
  }

  .about-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--ink-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-text strong {
    color: var(--cyan);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Cloud chips */
  .cloud-chips {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
    background: var(--surface-1);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-ghost);
    border-radius: var(--r-md);
  }

  .cloud-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .cloud-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .cloud-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    color: var(--ink-secondary);
    background: var(--surface-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--r-sm);
    padding: 2px var(--space-3);
    transition: color var(--t-fast), border-color var(--t-fast), background var(--t-fast);
  }

  .cloud-tag:hover {
    color: var(--cyan);
    border-color: var(--border-standard);
    background: var(--cyan-dim);
  }

  .cloud-tag--dev {
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    border-style: dashed;
  }

  /* Principles */
  .principles {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .principle-card {
    background: var(--surface-1);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-ghost);
    border-radius: var(--r-md);
    padding: var(--space-4);
    transition:
      border-color var(--t-mid),
      transform var(--t-mid);
  }

  .principle-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-subtle);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .principle-icon {
    color: var(--cyan);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .principle-card h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }

  .principle-card p {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--ink-tertiary);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .principle-card--cloud {
    border-color: var(--border-subtle);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.04), var(--surface-1));
  }

  .principle-card--cloud .principle-icon {
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-10);
    }
    .principles {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .principles {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 500px) {
    .principles {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
